arcade.agent.cell

Class TissueCCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.agent.cell.TissueCell
      • arcade.agent.cell.TissueHCell
        • arcade.agent.cell.TissueCCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cell, java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TissueSCell

    public class TissueCCell
extends TissueHCell
    Extension of TissueHCell for cancerous tissue cells.

    TissueCCell agents are modified from their superclass:

    • Code change to CODE_C_CELL
    • If cell is quiescent, they may exit out of quiescence into neutral if there is space in their neighborhood
    Since:
    2.2
    Version:
    2.2.7
